# FAF GO Demo - Guided Path to Gold Code
# VHS tape file - renders to GIF

# Configuration
Output demos/faf-go-demo.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

# Show the terminal
Type "# FAF GO - Guided Interview to Gold Code"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# Let's see our current score first"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "faf score"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Now let's use faf go to reach 100%!"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "faf go"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# In Claude Code, this returns structured JSON"
Enter
Type "# for AskUserQuestion - AI asks the questions!"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Try it: just type 'faf go' and answer questions"
Enter
Type "# till you hit Gold Code (100%)"
Enter
Sleep 2s
